OL,3,CA look back at Alex Salmond's career
OL,4,Cin Scottish politics
OL,6,FAlex Salmond was the preeminent
OL,7,Fpolitician of Scotland's devolution
OL,8,Fera.
OL,10,FNo other political leader, not even
OL,11,F'the father of devolution', Labour's
OL,12,FDonald Dewar who brought the Scottish
OL,13,Fparliament into existence, changed
OL,14,FScotland in the way Salmond did.
OL,16,FThe former First Minister took the
OL,17,FScottish National Party from the
OL,18,Ffringe of Caledonian politics -
OL,19,Fsometimes ridiculed, often ignored,
OL,20,Falways fighting to be taken seriously
OL,21,F- to power at Holyrood.
