OL,3,CA look back at Alex Salmond's career
OL,4,Cin Scottish politics
OL,6,FAnd more than that: he took Scotland
OL,7,Fto the brink of achieving his life-
OL,8,Flong ambition of breaking from the
OL,9,FUnited Kingdom and becoming an
OL,10,Findependent nation.
OL,12,FHe came far too close for comfort for
OL,13,Funionists, who had thought
OL,14,Findependence unthinkable; and so near
OL,15,Fand yet so far for nationalists who
OL,16,Fhad thought it inevitable.
