OL,3,CA look back at Alex Salmond's career
OL,4,Cin Scottish politics
OL,6,FIn simple, factual terms in the
OL,7,Findependence referendum of 18
OL,8,FSeptember 2014 he lost, the
OL,9,Findependence movement lost, by some
OL,10,F45% to 55%, on a huge turnout of Scots.
OL,12,FBut in defeat there was also a
OL,13,Fvictory. Far from ending the debate on
OL,14,Fself-government, it continued, with
OL,15,Fseveral huge election wins for the
OL,16,FSNP, often viewed as buyers remorse on
OL,17,Fthe part of Scottish voters.
