OL,3,CA look back at Alex Salmond's career
OL,4,Cin Scottish politics
OL,6,FThe recent election of a UK Labour
OL,7,Fgovernment, with a substantial revival
OL,8,Ffor the party in Scotland has, for now
OL,9,Fat least, put paid to any immediate
OL,10,Fhope of a second referendum and
OL,11,Findependence.
OL,13,FThough beware: modern politics can
OL,14,Fchange, and change very quickly. Much
OL,15,Fdepends on Keir Starmer's government,
OL,16,Fwhich has not been without its
OL,17,Ftroubles in its first 100 days in
OL,18,Foffice.
