OL,3,CA look back at Alex Salmond's career
OL,4,Cin Scottish politics
OL,6,FNevertheless, Salmond shifted the dial
OL,7,Fon the constitutional question. He won
OL,8,Fpower for the SNP as a minority
OL,9,Fgovernment at Holyrood, then won a
OL,10,Fmajority which gave him the mandate
OL,11,Ffor the referendum.
OL,13,FHe governed Scotland well, while
OL,14,Fleading the minority administration.
OL,15,FThere were some eye-catching policies,
OL,16,Fmixed with political pragmatism. The
OL,17,Fvoters noticed and gave him that all-
OL,18,Fimportant majority.
