OL,3,CA look back at Alex Salmond's career
OL,4,Cin Scottish politics
OL,6,FWhen he looked back on the referendum,
OL,7,FSalmond concluded that going from
OL,8,Fsignificantly behind in the polls to
OL,9,Fwinning was "a bridge too far", but he
OL,10,Fcertainly gave unionist opinion a very
OL,11,Fserious shock.
OL,13,FBut subsequent to the SNP's defeat,
OL,14,FWestminster legislated to make the
OL,15,FScottish parliament more powerful than
OL,16,Fit had been. Salmond left office with
OL,17,FHolyrood more powerful than when he
OL,18,Facceded to it.
