OL,3,CA look back at Alex Salmond's career
OL,4,Cin Scottish politics
OL,6,FHe resigned the day after the
OL,7,Freferendum, leaving his political ally
OL,8,FNicola Sturgeon, who he had mentored,
OL,9,Fto take over as party leader and First
OL,10,FMinister
OL,12,F.What has happened since the
OL,13,Freferendum has tarnished Salmond's
OL,14,Freputation. He could not resist the
OL,15,Fcall of politics and went back to
OL,16,FWestminster as an MP.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/14
