OL,3,CA look back at Alex Salmond's career
OL,4,Cin Scottish politics
OL,6,FHe tried hard to play the elder
OL,7,Fstatesman, but found that role hard,
OL,8,Fto Sturgeon's increasing frustration.
OL,9,FHe lost his seat, Gordon in the north-
OL,10,Feast of Scotland, in 2017.
OL,12,FHis parting shot, echoing a Jacobite
OL,13,Fsong, was "You've not seen the last of
OL,14,Fmy bonnets and me." And indeed we had
OL,15,Fnot, though not in the way Salmond had
OL,16,Fplanned.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G8/14
