OL,3,CA look back at Alex Salmond's career
OL,4,Cin Scottish politics
OL,6,FAfter a court case which took place in
OL,7,Fthe shadow of the growing Covid
OL,8,Fpandemic, in March 2020 Salmond was
OL,9,Fcleared by a jury at the High Court in
OL,10,FEdinburgh of attempted rape and a
OL,11,Fseries of sexual assaults, including
OL,12,Fone with intent to rape.He denied all
OL,13,F13 charges against nine women and the
OL,14,Fjury returned a not proven verdict on
OL,15,Fone charge of assault with intent to
OL,16,Frape, finding him not guilty of all
OL,17,Fother charges, including an attempted
OL,18,Frape.The details of that, and a
OL,19,Fsubsequent lawsuit against the
OL,20,FScottish government which he won, have
OL,21,Fbeen well documented but they led to
OL,22,Fan irrevocable falling out between
OL,23,FSalmond and Sturgeon.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G9/14
