OL,3,CA look back at Alex Salmond's career
OL,4,Cin Scottish politics
OL,6,FThe great alliance, sorcerer and
OL,7,Fapprentice, was shattered, and
OL,8,Fshattered for good, as both admitted.
OL,9,FThe independence movement shattered
OL,10,Ftoo as Salmond formed his own Alba
OL,11,Fparty.
OL,13,FLooking back on the referendum,
OL,14,FSalmond told my ITV Border colleague
OL,15,FMatty Sutton he wished he had not
OL,16,Fstood down as First Minister, bringing
OL,17,Fa scathing response from his successor.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G10/14
