OL,3,CA look back at Alex Salmond's career
OL,4,Cin Scottish politics
OL,6,FSo what of Salmond the man? During
OL,7,Fthat trial, Salmond's QC Gordon
OL,8,FJackson told the jury his client could
OL,9,Fhave been a "better man" but was not
OL,10,Fguilty of sexual offences.
OL,12,FSalmond subsequently himself said he
OL,13,Fwas "no saint." As a party leader and
OL,14,FFirst Minister he could be both
OL,15,Fdemanding and overbearing.
