OL,3,CA look back at Alex Salmond's career
OL,4,Cin Scottish politics
OL,6,FThose who he appointed, ministers and
OL,7,Fadvisers, say he gave them room to get
OL,8,Fon with their job, only becoming
OL,9,Fcritical and demanding when things
OL,10,Fwent wrong. Others who incurred his
OL,11,Fwrath take a very different view.
OL,13,FHe would not, though, be the first
OL,14,Fsenior politician whose behaviour
OL,15,Fwould seem, to many, unacceptable.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G12/14
