OL,3,CA look back at Alex Salmond's career
OL,4,Cin Scottish politics
OL,6,FThose who served him - and one of his
OL,7,Fstrengths was to employ highly skilled
OL,8,Fand able people - argue how effective
OL,9,Fhe was. They loved him. Yes, loved
OL,10,Fhim. Many of his staff were in tears
OL,11,Fwhen he resigned.
OL,13,FIt is often said that journalists
OL,14,Fwrite the first draft of history. If
OL,15,Fthat is so, it is only a very rough
OL,16,Fdraft. Proper analysis of the impact
OL,17,Fand legacy of Alex Salmond must be
OL,18,Fleft to academia.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G13/14
