OL,3,CA look back at Alex Salmond's career
OL,4,Cin Scottish politics
OL,6,FHowever, from the viewpoint of this
OL,7,Fjournalist, who has followed the ebb
OL,8,Fand flow of Scottish politics since
OL,9,Fbefore devolution, the late First
OL,10,FMinister was a pivotal figure.
OL,12,FAlex Salmond changed the course of
OL,13,FScottish political history. Whether
OL,14,Fthat is for good or ill is quite
OL,15,Fanother matter.
OL,17,FHave you heard our podcast Talking
OL,18,FPolitics? Tom, Robert and Anushka dig
OL,19,Finto the biggest issues dominating the
OL,20,Fpolitical agenda in every episode...
